In [12]:
color_array = []
for structure_id, coords in calpha_dict.items():
    activity = dict_activity.get(structure_id, 'unknown')
    if activity == 'active':
        color_array.extend(['red'] * len(coords))
    elif activity == 'inactive':
        color_array.extend(['blue'] * len(coords))
    else:
        color_array.extend(['grey'] * len(coords))

len(color_array)
